          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The <strong class="text-text">Malawi National Electronic Procurement System (MANEPS)</strong> is the government's e-procurement platform. The 2025 Act mandates its use (s.38(5), s.71), and a Ministry of Finance directive requires <strong class="text-text">all government PDEs to use MANEPS from 1 April 2026</strong>.
